Package: textpress
Type: Package
Title: A lightweight, unobtrusive R companion for basic NLP.
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Jason Timm [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jason Timm <JaTimm@salud.unm.edu>
Description: A lightweight, versatile NLP companion in R. The package provides features for (1) basic text processing, (2) corpus search, and (3) web scraping.  Additionally included are utility functions for (4) building text embeddings via the HuggingFace API, and (5) fetching chat completions via the OpenAI API.  
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    httr,
    Matrix,
    rvest,
    stringi, 
    jsonlite,
    stringr,
    xml2,
    pbapply
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
